---
import '../styles/global.css';
const phone = '(803) 530-4489';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>A-1 Backflow Specialties | Certified Backflow Testing</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A-1 Backflow Specialties provides certified backflow testing for residential, commercial, and municipal customers." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="A-1 Backflow Specialties" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="The best backflow specialist for certified backflow testing, reporting, and service." />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#a7d8f0" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="topbar"><div class="container"><span>Certified Backflow Testing • Residential • Commercial • Municipal</span><a href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>{phone}</a></div></div>
    <header class="site-header"><div class="container nav"><a class="brand" href="#top"><span class="logo">A-1</span><span>A-1 Backflow Specialties</span></a><nav class="links"><a href="#services">Services</a><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a><a href="#process">Process</a><a href="#faq">FAQ</a><a href="#contact">Contact</a><a class="button blue" href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>Call Now</a></nav></div></header>
    <main id="top">
      <section class="hero"><div class="container hero-grid"><div><p class="eyebrow">Pantone 291 C • Certified Testing</p><h1>The Best Backflow Specialist.</h1><p class="lead">Expert BackFlow Solutions for annual testing, reporting, and service. A cleaner, faster, more professional online home for A-1 Backflow Specialties.</p><div style="display:flex;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:1.4rem"><a class="button blue" href="#contact">Schedule Your Test</a><a class="button ghost" href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>Call {phone}</a></div><div class="stats"><div class="stat"><strong>$45</strong><span>Residential</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>$60</strong><span>Commercial</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>A+</strong><span>Trust-focused</span></div></div></div><div class="hero-card"><div class="fake-photo"><div class="photo-panel"><strong>Protect your drinking water.</strong><br/>Certified backflow testing with reports handled the right way.</div></div></div></div></section>
      <section id="services" class="section"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">Services</p><h2>Backflow testing made simple.</h2><p>Keep the existing message, but present it clearly: schedule, test, file, done.</p></div><div class="grid-3"><div class="card"><h3>Residential</h3><p>Annual backflow testing for irrigation systems and residential devices.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Commercial</h3><p>Certified testing and documentation for businesses, facilities, and properties.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Municipal</h3><p>Professional reporting and compliance support for water utility requirements.</p></div></div></div></section>
      <section id="pricing" class="section" style="background:white"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">Pricing</p><h2>Clear pricing. No clutter.</h2></div><div class="grid-3"><div class="card"><h3>Residential</h3><div class="price">$45</div><p>Certified test and report.</p><a class="button blue" href="#contact">Schedule</a></div><div class="card"><h3>Commercial</h3><div class="price">$60</div><p>Certified commercial testing.</p><a class="button blue" href="#contact">Schedule</a></div><div class="card"><h3>Need Help?</h3><p>Not sure what device you have or whether your report is due?</p><a class="button ghost" href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>Call A-1</a></div></div></div></section>
      <section id="process" class="section"><div class="container split"><div><p class="eyebrow">Process</p><h2>Schedule. Test. Report. Done.</h2><p>A simple process helps customers understand that backflow testing does not need to be complicated.</p></div><div class="panel"><ul class="checklist"><li>Schedule your annual backflow test</li><li>A certified tester completes the test</li><li>Required reporting is prepared</li><li>Your water utility receives what it needs</li></ul></div></div></section>
      <section id="faq" class="section faq" style="background:white"><div class="container"><div class="section-head"><p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p><h2>Common questions.</h2></div><details open><summary>Do I need annual backflow testing?</summary><p>Many water providers require annual testing for backflow prevention assemblies.</p></details><details><summary>Do I need to be home?</summary><p>That depends on device location and access. Call A-1 to confirm.</p></details><details><summary>Can you submit the report?</summary><p>The site should clearly state reporting support so customers know the job is handled end-to-end.</p></details></div></section>
      <section id="contact" class="section cta"><div class="container split"><div><p class="eyebrow">Contact</p><h2>Ready to schedule?</h2><p>Use this section for phone, email, service area, and the live contact form once connected.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>A-1 Backflow Specialties</h3><p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>{phone}</a></p><p><strong>Service:</strong> Backflow testing, reporting, and compliance support.</p><a class="button blue" href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>Call Now</a></div></div></section>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer"><div class="container footer-grid"><div><h3>A-1 Backflow Specialties</h3><p>Modernized website draft using Pantone 291 C as the brand color.</p></div><div><strong>Navigate</strong><p><a href="#services">Services</a><br/><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a><br/><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></p></div><div><strong>Contact</strong><p>{phone}</p></div></div></footer>
    <a class="button blue mobile-call" href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')}`}>Call {phone}</a>
  </body>
</html>
